2017-07-16 - Version 1.2.1 ***

* Made asteroid collision physics on by default
* Added config file support for Windows and Linux

2017-07-15 - Version 1.2.0 ***

* Added Windows support
* User can change initial asteroid count with '-i' switch
* Randomized asteroid spawn size
* Improved asteroid collision physics

2017-07-11 - Version 1.1.0 ***

* Added asteroid collision physics with other asteroids
* User can enable asteroid collisions with '-p' switch

2017-07-06 - Version 1.0.1 ***

* Made physics independent of framerate
* Added support for arbitrary number of asteroids
* Added command line argument parsing
* Added usage and version info
* User can change maximum asteroid count with '-n' switch
* User can change Vsync/swap interval with '-s' switch

2017-07-02 - Version 1.0.0 ***

* Initial release

